# Beer Label Generator

This project provides a printable HTML5 beer label generator. Enter the beer style and bottling date to populate 18 labels (3 across Ã— 6 down) that fit neatly on an A4 sheet. Print the page using your browser's print dialog.

## Getting started

Open `index.html` in any modern browser. Fill in the form and click **Print** when you're ready to produce a sheet of labels.
